  ID: MenAtArms
  Name: "La Valette\u2019s guard"
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: "He survived two campaigns and thought faith insulated guts from fate.
    A musket ball entered above his navel and tore intestine \u2014 now he leaks
    his own waste into his abdomen. He asks for water; it only worsens his swelling.\n\nTreatment:
    No stitching can save intestine in 1565. You pour wine into the wound to slow
    rot. Pack with poultice. Keep him warm; death is a matter of hours or days."
